# Bloodsucker Localization

## Role Greeting
bloodsucker-role-greeting = You are a Bloodsucker, an immortal creature of the night!
    Feed on the blood of the living to sustain your powers.
    Avoid sunlight at all costs - it will burn you to ash.
    Find a coffin to rest and regenerate your blood reserves.
    Use your powers wisely to hunt, convert thralls, and survive the night.

## Ability Messages
bloodsucker-ability-glare = You glare at your victim, freezing them in place!
bloodsucker-ability-glare-target = You are frozen by an unnatural gaze!
bloodsucker-ability-cloak-on = You fade into darkness...
bloodsucker-ability-cloak-off = You become visible again.
bloodsucker-ability-drain-start = You sink your fangs into your victim!
bloodsucker-ability-drain-target = You feel your blood being drained!
bloodsucker-ability-drain-finish = You finish draining blood!
bloodsucker-ability-thrall-start = You begin to enthrall your victim...
bloodsucker-ability-thrall-target = Your mind is being invaded!
bloodsucker-ability-thrall-finish = You have enthralled {$target}!
bloodsucker-ability-thrall-target-finish = You feel an overwhelming loyalty to your master...

## Coffin Messages
bloodsucker-coffin-enter = You rest in the coffin, feeling your power slowly return...

